What circumstances or people in your life are difficult for you to accept? What can you do to co-exist with the discomfort and achieve contentment. \
\
Circumstance difficult to accept is my bad back and that it cost me freedom, sports, masculinity, youth. New boss was difficult to accept. To co-exist with new boss I sought counsel from a wise brother who helped me reframe, let go and embrace being of service to the boss as part of the team. Contentment with my back will come once i have done all i can to improve the situation. Lose weight, exercise, become a man I have never been. As i improve, lowering the roadblocks that my back imposed on my life. Difficult to accept that a loved one may not like me anymore, resents that I am not there for them through tough times. I can block this out with belief that they one day will not resent me.\
