Own his own business - Took on much greater responsibility, cost time away from kids, cost marriage, cost friendships. Inherit wealth - Pre-occupied with keeping/protecting it, never fully embraced a shared life with partners who eventually left. Does what he wants - has life without meaning and growth and looks tragic in old age. \
